# This repo is the agent ROOT: `agent pull` clones every reachable repo as a
# sibling directory here, and each carries its own .git and venvs. Without an
# allowlist the build context is hundreds of megabytes of unrelated checkouts.
#
# Deny everything, then re-include exactly what the Dockerfile COPYs.
*
!agent
!agentcli/
!issue_agent/
!pyproject.toml
!README.md

# Re-included dirs still drag these in.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
